name: Warring Seers of the Runic Stars
description: Hailing from the Osmerian Sea, the Warring Seers of the Runic Stars are known for their prowess with nearly any form of arms. One of the few who witnessed the Osmerian Anomaly, and equipped with the knowledge of what may have actually happened, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
